These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, sports, crime
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, tiparillo, cain, aristoff
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | crime | sports |
| Cigar        | pall-mall | tiparillo   | aristoff | cain    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, cain, bluemaster, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, house, hip-hop, classical
1. the cain-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of blues is the game-smoker##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the fan of blues is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | game  | cain  | bolivar |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | blues | hip-hop | house    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dannemann, aristoff, blend
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, skateboard, boat, roller
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
2. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Cigar          | blend | aristoff | dannemann    | bongani      |
| Transport   | boat        | roller     | train | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, chess, scrabble
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, mirinda, iced-tea
1. the person playing backgammon is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game         | scrabble | whist | backgammon | chess |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | milk   | coffee    | iced-tea  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
City: boston, paris, venice, miami
4 different pets are kept: horse, bird, snake, pony
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
6. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| City   | paris  | boston    | venice   | miami       |
| Pet   | horse | pony | snake | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, pear, grapefruit, pepper
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | grapefruit      | pear | pepper | pumpkin |
| Flower   | amaryllis | marigold     | tulip  | balloon-flower  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, corn, lettuce, kiwi
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, purple, green, apricot
1. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person who likes apricot is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
6. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | raspberry | kiwi | lettuce | corn    |
| Color     | apricot | green  | chestnut     | purple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, april, may
House: cottage, farmhouse, craftsman, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
7. the farmhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in august and the craftsman house##2
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Birthday   | november | august      | may | april |
| House   | cottage  | futuristic | farmhouse    | craftsman            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
City: paris, hannover, boston, berlin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, thriller, horror, animation
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person watching family movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person traveling to boston##2
4. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to boston is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | berlin | hannover   | paris | boston |
| Movie-Genre    | animation     | thriller | family     | horror  |

