.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, cooking, puzzles, writing
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cranberry, onion, eggplant
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person eating eggplant is between the person eating nectarine and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | cooking       | puzzles   | dancing | writing |
| Food   | onion | cranberry | eggplant        | nectarine    |

