2. the game-smoker is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the game-smoker is on the left of the musical-polo-smoker##1
4. the musical-polo-smoker is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | musical   | action      | superhero      |
| Cigar      | cain | game | musical-polo | tiparillo |

