.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, software-developer, lawyer, electrician
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, bus, train
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
3. the software-developer is in an even position##4
4. the analyst is on the far right##1
5. the lawyer is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job          | electrician | software-developer  | lawyer  | analyst |
| Transport   | train  | bus | motorbike | helicopter   |

