.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, golf, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, train, tram
1. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
6. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Sport   | golf | skiing | ice-hockey | lacrosse |
| Transport           | tram     | bus     | train   | van         |

