.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, cherry, spinach, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, blues, trance, gospel
1. the person eating mango is between the fan of hip-hop and the person eating cherry##2
2. the person eating spinach is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating cherry is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
5. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Food   | nectarine | cherry         | mango   | spinach |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | blues | gospel | hip-hop   |

