.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, orchid, rose, azalea
House: ranch-style, victorian, futuristic, palace
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
3. the victorian house is the person who growsrose##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
5. the victorian house is between the palace house and the futuristic house##2
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Flower         | azalea   | rose | sunflower | orchid    |
| House   | futuristic | victorian  | palace     | ranch-style |

