.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, fish, lizard
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, german, spanish, thai
1. the german is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is on the left of the thai##1
5. the thai is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the spanish is in an even position##4
7. the malaysian is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Pet   | lizard | goat    | fish       | ferret |
| Nationality       | german  | spanish | thai | malaysian  |

