.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, art-deco, wooden
There 4 different types of food: mango, lettuce, artichoke, corn
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the wooden house##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
6. the person eating mango is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | ranch-style | art-deco | cape-cod  | wooden |
| Food     | mango      | artichoke       | lettuce | corn     |

