.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, camping, traveling, drawing
City: venice, colone, new-york, san-francisco
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
3. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person traveling to venice##2
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | traveling   | drawing | camping |
| City   | san-francisco          | colone | venice         | new-york  |

 